@startuml
actor "Child (User)" as User
participant "UI Button" as UI
participant "Game Engine" as Game
participant "Speech Manager" as Speech
participant "Web Speech API" as API

User -> UI: Click "Fireball" spell
UI -> Game: Trigger spell selection
Game -> Speech: Start listening (target: "Fireball")
Speech -> API: Request microphone & stream
API --> Speech: Return transcript "Fireball"
Speech -> Game: Validate: "Fireball" == "Fireball"
Game -> UI: Play animation & damage enemy
Game -> Game: Save progress to LocalStorage
@enduml